data.description: Buyers, don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity as the sellers are moving due to a job transfer, making this home an incredible find - Impressive 2-story basement home w/over 4750 sqft. of spacious, light & bright living space in highly rated Cuthbertson Schools.Upgrades include fresh interior & exterior paint, LVP flooring & carpeting. Main level offers a formal living & dining area , a well-appointed office, and oversized family room that seamlessly connects to the gourmet kitchen that boasts granite countertops, stainless steel appliances & butler's pantry. Plus a deck off the kitchen, providing a delightful outdoor extension for dining & relaxation . 2nd floor offers primary bedroom suite w/tray ceiling,sitting area and spacious primary bath , 3 secondary BRs + Bonus/Bedroom totaling 5 BRs-.Fully finished basement is an entertainer's dream w/home movie theatre/game room,billiard/rec room,wet bar,exercise room & 2 storage rooms w/an additional bed/bath to complete this level.
